    {% call components.columnTwoThirds() %}

        <p>This topic covers the role unconscious bias can play in the workplace, as well as the importance of equality, diversity and inclusion.</p>

        <p>You also learn about the equality laws that are in place, and the duty to treat our customers fairly.</p>
        <p>This diversity and inclusion topic contains 8 activities. You can do them all in one go or in stages. </p>

        {{ components.heading(text='Learning outcomes', tag='h2', size='medium') }}

        <p>On completing all the topics, you'll:</p>
        <ul class="list-bullet u-space-b30">
            <li>have an understanding of what unconscious bias is and how it can affect your work</li>
            <li>be able to recognise different types of unconscious bias and their impact</li>
            <li>know how to challenge your own thinking, and how to help create the right environment.</li>
            <li>be aware of some of the strategies you can use to minimise the impact of unconscious bias on decision making</li>
            <li>understand why we need legislation</li>
            <li>be more aware of how stereotyping, bullying and harassment can affect work relationships and decisions</li>
            <li>have insight into the barriers disabled customers may face and duties towards all of our customers</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>You must complete all 8 learning modules to finish this topic.</strong></p>

